label ch1:
    # $ skip_next = "skip_to_ch2"
    scene black
    show bg bg2 with Dissolve(2)
    show abd normal at left
    with dissolve
    show jaf normal at right
    with dissolve
    show jaf smile at right
    jaf "Ah, my beloved Agrabah."
    show jaf normal at right
    jaf "What's this smell? Crazy Hakim?"
    show abd alert at left
    abd "No, it's from all the garbage in the alleys."
    show abd normal at left
    abd "Nobody is collecting them."
    abd "They say that you betrayed the Sultan. They say you returned and tried to kill him."
    abd "But things were better when you were in charge."
    abd "After you 'left', everyone stopped doing their jobs."
    show jaf thinking at right
    jaf "What else do they say about me?"
    abd "That they destroyed you by destroying your lamp."
    show jaf normal at right
    jaf "Ah, that. They tried, but turns out Genies can't die."
    show jaf annoyed at right
    jaf "After a painful while, my lamp just appeared where you found me."
    jaf "Where the Cave of Wonders was."
    show jaf normal at right
    show abd confused at left
    abd "Cave of wonders?"
    jaf "You don't know much about what happened, do you?"
    show abd normal at left
    abd "I was there when the Genie picked up the palace and put in on the hilltop."
    abd "They said you commanded him."
    abd "And I've heard some things from the palace guards here and there."
    abd "Usually everything happens inside the palace walls when nobody is around."
    show jaf thinking at right
    jaf "Interesting. you should tell me those stories at some point."
    jaf "Is the Sultan still alive?"
    show jaf normal at right
    abd "Yes, the Sultan retired and gave the throne to Aladdin and Jasmine."
    abd "He's the new sultan that is always out of the city flying his carpet."
    show jaf annoyed at right
    jaf "And Jasmine have no clue how to rule. I knew it."
    jaf "I'll deal with this later, for now we have a bigger fish to catch."
    show jaf normal at right
    show abd sad at left
    abd "..."
    jaf "What?"
    abd "My fish business..."
    show jaf annoyed at right
    jaf "Snap out of it. Abdul. A whole new life is in front of you."
    show jaf normal at right
    show abd alert at left
    jaf "First we need to deal with our most urgent problem, we can't be seen like this."
    jaf "Let's go to your house.{w=.5} This way?"
    show abd sad at left
    abd "No."
    jaf "Aha? you don't live near bazaar anymore? This way?"
    abd "No."
    show jaf annoyed at right
    jaf "Which way then?"
    abd "No way."
    show jaf disappointed at right
    jaf "You've lost your house too?"
    abd "Yes, I've been living on the streets."
    show jaf normal at right
    jaf "How unfortunate, but lucky for you, I know a place, and I'm sure it's vacant too."
    show abd confused at left
    jaf "Its resident moved to a bigger place."
    jaf "Follow me."
    jump ch2